{"tid":895236,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：山齊士已失信心 強項都無法發揮出來","createTime":"2018-11-09T04:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T05:10:01.000Z","uid":37168,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"99ab3fb220817bbc746fd890191080d96bce46da","tid":895236,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"山齊士自從冬窗加盟曼聯以來一直比較低迷，拿著英超第一週薪，表現卻配不上身價，這讓他遭到了不少非議。山齊士昔日的恩師雲格在接受採訪時也表達了自己的觀點，雲格認為曼聯的山齊士有些失去信心了。<br />\n<br />\n雲格接受beIN Sports採訪時說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我覺得山齊士有些失去信心了。</span>他的強項是盤帶和過人。當球員失去信心的時候是最脆弱的<span style=\"color: red;\">。因為比賽中的表現就是基於信心和積極性，他慢慢的失去了這些。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n「賽季開始的時候他身體狀況很好，但是之後有些下降。當然摩連奴都雪藏了他一段時間，現在我認為他已經恢復了。」<br />\n<br />\n在盧卡古受傷後，山齊士近期都作為曼聯的正選中鋒出戰，表現可圈可點。不過面對祖雲達斯的比賽中，山齊士出現了受傷的狀況。《郵報》的消息稱，還不確定他能否出戰本週末的曼市打吡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7d6721f3f19b00ae844242de859277a7bef24d","tid":895236,"uid":18646,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"爺爺：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c329447b2e0b96de4373316ba4f7a38aa7ff0d","tid":895236,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6b3ec61604e1f4bad641d22ca021e51b24bf2d","tid":895236,"uid":41658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"撚摩狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f195f98eb075bad94771f5862d71002